Khmer Legal Codes (KLC) is a mobile application designed to help users conveniently explore publicly available legal and justice information in Cambodia. It serves as an educational and reference tool for the general public, students, lawyers, court officials, prosecutors, judges, and other legal professionals who want easier access to trusted legal resources.

Sources of Information
KLC compiles and organizes information from publicly available government publications, official gazettes, the Samdech Joon Nath Dictionary, law books, and other reliable public sources. All content is for informational and educational purposes only.

Disclaimer
KLC is an independent application and is not affiliated with, endorsed by, or representing any government entity in Cambodia. The app does not provide official government services.

Key Features
• Legal Search – Search for laws, articles, and legal notes using keywords or article references. Includes publicly available codes of procedure, laws, and regulations.
• Legal Dictionary – Look up legal terms with clear explanations from official publications, dictionaries, and law books.
• Research – Access scanned or digital versions of original legal documents in PDF format for study and reference.
• Legal Analysis – Read educational summaries and commentaries prepared by independent legal scholars.
• Presentations – Browse and view educational presentations based on legal lessons or articles.
• Videos – Watch explanatory videos related to specific laws and legal topics.
• News & Updates – Follow public announcements and updates relevant to Cambodia’s legal sector.
• Location Finder – Search for and locate courts, legal offices, and professional services.
• Legal Consultation – Submit questions for general legal guidance and educational purposes.

Our Mission
KLC’s goal is to make legal information easier to find, understand, and use—supporting public awareness of the law in Cambodia.

developer: Legal Council of Ministry of Economy and Finance
description:
This application provides us a great tool for accessing the Legal Lexicon for Ministry of Economy and Finance of Cambodia which is published as book in 2021.

The legal terms are organized by Khmer alphabetical order with its single or multiple sectors, legal definitions and references which provide ease for user to find the source of the keyword.

Importantly, with this application, it facilitates user in searching keywords with possible link to other keywords and also references that we can consult immediately the sources which can be laws and regulations. At the same time of searching, for later use, the application records as well the list of keywords that user used to search. More advanced than this, user also can search keywords by sectors such as taxation, state property, public finance, ... etc.

For viewing detail explanation of keywords, the explanation consists of keyword that user is willing to view, its sector and its definitions. This explanation font size can be increased or decreased for ease of use. Also we can view the next and previous keyword by scroll left or right or with the bottom left and right buttons.

In addition, there is a useful tutorial for helping user to know how to use this application which will tell us all about its features.
